    <abstract>
      <t>This document is a report on an Internet architecture workshop, initiated by the IAB and held at MCI on October 12-14, 1994.  This workshop generally focused on aspects of the information infrastructure on the Internet.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.
